column.name: blocking_lock_duration
column.remarks: Lock duration. One of EXPLICIT (locks released by explicit action, for example a global lock acquired with FLUSH TABLES WITH READ LOCK) , STATEMENT (locks implicitly released at statement end) or TRANSACTION (locks implicitly released at transaction end).
